enumDescriptions: The command type was unspecified.
Reboot the device. Can only be issued to Kiosk and managed guest session devices.
Take a screenshot of the device. Only available if the device is in Kiosk Mode.
Set the volume of the device. Can only be issued to Kiosk and managed guest session devices.

payload.description: The payload for the command, provide it only if command supports it. If a device is being used, ackedUserPresence must be set to true to acknowledge that you want to start a CRD session anyways. It is false by default, so a CRD command will fail if used on an active device without this field.
